imes which he claimed that there was close analogy between structure mark human brain his article included interview with turing who added this only foretaste what come only shadow what going be we have have some experience with machine before we really know its capabilities may take years before we settle down new possibilities but i do not see why should not enter any fields normally covered by human intellect eventually compete on equal terms see also information technology portal history computing hardware list vacuum tube computers manchester computers references notes b c lavington p b c d manchester mark university manchester retrieved january turing m on computable numbers with application entscheidungsproblem pdf proceedings london mathematical society published 1936–37 pp 230–265 doi101112/plms/s2-421230 lee p lavington p enticknap nicholas summer computing's golden jubilee resurrection bulletin computer conservation society issn 0958-7403 retrieved april early electronic computers 1946–51 university manchester retrieved november lavington p lavington p b c d lavington p lavington p newman's contribution mark machines university manchester retrieved january b c d napper r b e manchester mark university manchester retrieved january lavington s h july manchester mark atlas historical perspective pdf university central florida retrieved february reprint paper published communications acm january manchester mark i university manchester retrieved january b kilburn tom university manchester universal high-speed digital computing machine university manchester retrieved february reprint kilburn tom university manchester universal high-speed digital computing machine nature b c lavington p lavington pp 17–18 leavitt p leavitt p b programmers' handbook 2nd edition for manchester electronic computer mark ii university manchester retrieved january napper p lavington p lavington pp 24–25 burton christopher p baby's legacy – early manchester mainframes doc university ma